140.body: Git Source Inherits: ISplitMain , Ownable Author: @SonaEngineering; forked from 0xSplits will@0xSplits.xyz A composable and gas-efficient protocol for deploying splitter contracts. Split recipients, ownerships, and keeper fees are stored onchain as calldata & re-passed as args / validated via hashing when needed. Each split gets its own address & proxy for maximum composability with other contracts onchain. For these proxies, we extended EIP-1167 Minimal Proxy Contract to avoid DELEGATECALL inside receive() to accept hard gas-capped sends & transfers.
140.title: SplitMain
